flowchart LR
    subgraph fds["epoll fds"]
        Wake[wake_fd]
        StateTimer[state_timer_fd]
        Tick[tick_fd]
        ScenTimer[scenario_timer_fd]
    end

    Queue[(Event queue)]
    FSM["fsm::v2::FSM&lt;StateBase&gt;"]
    Ctx[FsmContext / SimVars]
    Ramp[RampInterpolator]
    Soc[SocIntegrator]
    Scen[ScenarioDispatcher]

    Wake --> Queue
    Queue --> FSM
    StateTimer -->|StateDeadline| FSM
    Tick --> Ramp
    Tick --> Soc
    ScenTimer --> Scen
    Scen -->|enqueue| Queue
    FSM <--> Ctx
    Ramp --> Ctx
    Soc --> Ctx
